Titolo: Baldo: The Guardian Owls

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Baldo: The Guardian Owls is an action-adventure role-playing video game developed and published by NAPS team. It was released for Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Microsoft Windows, iOS, and macOS. The Switch version of the game was scheduled to be released first in summer 2020 as a timed console exclusive, but the game was indefinitely delayed in September of that year. The game was released on August 27, 2021.Inspired by The Legend of Zelda and Studio Ghibli's films, it is an action adventure RPG, with puzzles, exploration and combat, set in a crafted hand-drawn open world.

Genere: Action-adventure 

Valutazione: 55
